                    "title": "Problem Statement",
                    "content": [
                        {
                            "type": "text",
                            "text": "Write a method to return all subsets of a set. The solution set must not contain duplicate subsets. Elements in a subset must be in non-descending order. The order of subsets in the result does not matter. **Example:** ``` Input: nums = [1,2,3] Output: [ [3],  [1],  [2],  [1,2,3],  [1,3],  [2,3],  [1,2],  [] ] ``` **Note:** `1 <= nums.length <= 10`"
                        }
                    ]
